00:08:29.476 --> 00:08:31.166 A:middle
application to run in the

00:08:31.166 --> 00:08:34.746 A:middle
background when the workout is

00:08:36.366 --> 00:08:36.515 A:middle
active.

00:08:36.716 --> 00:08:39.316 A:middle
